The test class JavaFishTest. This Test class is used to test that JavaFish function and instantiate correctly. Based on Dr Marc Price's LionTest from his video lesson on Blackboard.

Version:
23-02-2021, 0.2 Test Conditions: JavaFish(): CHECK that the speed has been automatically set between 0.005 - 0.05.
